Configuration.OOBJustification:
Per US91, operations allowed in the band 1755-1780 MHz at specific sites in US&P as follows:
Yuma Proving Ground, AZ;
Fort Irwin, CA;
Fort Polk, LA;
Fort Bragg, NC;
White Sands Missile Range, NM;
Fort Hood, TX

